Detailed Description

cvmx_uahc::_ehci_insnreg00

EHCI_INSNREG00 = EHCI Programmable Microframe Base Value Register (Synopsys Speicific) This register allows you to change the microframe length value (default is microframe SOF = 125 s) to reduce the simulation time.
